OL,7,FDr Emily Cooper says more needs to be
OL,8,Fdone to support bereaved parents five
OL,9,Fmonths on since her two-year-old
OL,10,Fdaughter's death.
OL,12,FA mother-of-four who lost two children
OL,13,Fto the same rare genetic condition
OL,14,Fsays the fear of losing another child
OL,15,Fis "paralysing" as she calls for more
OL,16,Fresearch into sudden childhood death.
OL,18,FDr Emily Cooper's two-year-old
OL,19,Fdaughter Isabelle died in September
OL,20,F2024, three years after she lost her
OL,21,Fthree-year-old son Alexander.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
