OL,4,Cdisorder 'paralysed' at fear of losing
OL,5,Cmore
OL,7,FThe family, from Lancaster, did not
OL,8,Ffind out Alexander had the PPA2
OL,9,Fmutation until nearly two years after
OL,10,Fhis death, and it was only then they
OL,11,Fdiscovered Isabelle also had it.
OL,13,FHer two surviving children are not at
OL,14,Frisk, although her other daughter
OL,15,FSophia is a carrier, but she says the
OL,16,Ffear of losing another child is
OL,17,F"torture" and believes bereaved
OL,18,Ffamilies need more support and access
OL,19,Fto genetic testing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
