OL,3,CMum who lost two children to rare
OL,4,Cdisorder 'paralysed' at fear of losing
OL,5,Cmore
OL,7,F"I can't explain the torture of having
OL,8,Fno explanation, not for just what
OL,9,Fhappened for the child that has died
OL,10,Fbut what could happen to the
OL,11,Fsiblings," Emily explains.
OL,13,F"It (genetic testing) is not happening
OL,14,Facross the board, so that is really
OL,15,Fsomething that needs to be pushed for
OL,16,Fand something families should not have
OL,17,Fto advocate for.
