OL,3,CMum who lost two children to rare
OL,4,Cdisorder 'paralysed' at fear of losing
OL,5,Cmore
OL,7,F"We are doing enough trying to cope
OL,8,Fjust getting out of bed. We need pro-
OL,9,Factive support from professionals -
OL,10,Fthat is a really important message."
OL,12,FWhat is the PPA2 mutation?
OL,14,FThe PPA2 mutation is a genetic variant
OL,15,Fand rare type of sudden arrhythmia
OL,16,Fsyndrome.
OL,18,FThis deficiency can cause sudden
OL,19,Fcardiac death (SCD) and other
OL,20,Fconditions in children, infants, and
OL,21,Fyoung adults
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
