OL,4,Cdisorder 'paralysed' at fear of losing
OL,5,Cmore
OL,7,FEmily, a senior lecturer in the UCLan
OL,8,Fschool of law and policing, who
OL,9,Fcarries the recessive gene along with
OL,10,Fher husband, has spoken openly about
OL,11,Fher grief online and has campaigned
OL,12,Ffor better awareness of sudden
OL,13,Fchildhood death and the PPA2
OL,14,Fdeficiency, a mitochondrial disease.
OL,16,FShe said: "It wasn't a conscious
OL,17,Fchoice, this was a void I needed to
OL,18,Fscream into. Had I not had that
OL,19,Fcommunity of support I don't know what
OL,20,FI would have done without it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
