OL,4,Cdisorder 'paralysed' at fear of losing
OL,5,Cmore
OL,7,F"You really need proactive
OL,8,Fprofessionals to help you deal with
OL,9,Fthe grief and trauma of losing a
OL,10,Fchild," Emily goes on to say.
OL,12,FThanks to that genetic testing they
OL,13,Fknow her five-year-old son Freddie is
OL,14,Fnot affected, and her daughter Sophia
OL,15,Fis a carrier which may affect her if
OL,16,Fshe has children.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
